 I have been thinking about Bryan’s Complan, and would like to change it so that he gets commissioned and on all Enterprise deals (also through channel). I think this is important as it sends a message that he is an important part of building the NA team, not just an inside sales guy (which he isn’t) and as such will be part of the success of NA number, so shares the same goal of $1.5M.
